{"tid":1163594,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"早排去咗首爾《防彈新人王》介紹嘅友貞食堂（又名姨母食堂），食咗個防彈套餐，感到滿足！","createTime":"2019-05-20T14:02:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T09:58:33.000Z","uid":76632,"like":24,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"43072af4a62cf47618e54d10acfc4de839802f0a","tid":1163594,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T14:02:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://iill.li/iiḷlḷịị\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fiill.li%2Fii%E1%B8%B7l%E1%B8%B7%E1%BB%8B%E1%BB%8B&h=9535bed5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://iill.li/iiḷlḷlị\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fiill.li%2Fii%E1%B8%B7l%E1%B8%B7l%E1%BB%8B&h=9506ef1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://iill.li/iiḷlḷll\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fiill.li%2Fii%E1%B8%B7l%E1%B8%B7ll&h=69896bd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://iill.li/iiḷlḷlḷ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fiill.li%2Fii%E1%B8%B7l%E1%B8%B7l%E1%B8%B7&h=685bd2d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://iill.li/iiḷiịiiii\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fiill.li%2Fii%E1%B8%B7i%E1%BB%8Biiii&h=20262537&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://iill.li/iiḷiịiiiị\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fiill.li%2Fii%E1%B8%B7i%E1%BB%8Biii%E1%BB%8B&h=6ebd6d79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n先貼住少少圖。<br />\n<br />\n文字後補，內容包括:<br />\n1. 訪問店長（姨母）點睇bts及army，<br />\n2. 隔離幾枱army（有鬼妹、台妹、東南亞妹等等）對bts嘅感受，<br />\n3. 防彈套餐（黑豬肉泡菜撈飯）食評。"},{"pid":"5e5d3ca45bc2be587c53eb654f16c79fcc7db2fc","tid":1163594,"uid":76632,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T14:05:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://iill.li/iiḷiịiiil\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fiill.li%2Fii%E1%B8%B7i%E1%BB%8Biiil&h=17f8d505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://iill.li/iiḷiịiiiḷ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fiill.li%2Fii%E1%B8%B7i%E1%BB%8Biii%E1%B8%B7&h=93e050b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://iill.li/iiḷiịiiịi\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fiill.li%2Fii%E1%B8%B7i%E1%BB%8Bii%E1%BB%8Bi&h=a506d348&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://iill.li/iiḷiịiiịị\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fiill.li%2Fii%E1%B8%B7i%E1%BB%8Bii%E1%BB%8B%E1%BB%8B&h=92c4da49&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fbca341f821778ea1b5f709389703be44bb9bf8b","tid":1163594,"uid":52122,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T14:09:05.000Z","msg":"第一睇到 以為佢死撚左俾人供奉個啲靈堂咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16a377ed73b1af0273219635b9e002ce904fae31","tid":1163594,"uid":76632,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"fbca341f821778ea1b5f709389703be44bb9bf8b","tid":1163594,"uid":52122,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T14:09:05.000Z","msg":"第一睇到 以為佢死撚左俾人供奉個啲靈堂咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T14:11:27.000Z","msg":"No, not today"},{"pid":"2af014d2a4b1b2715c65bebf0e3e848f9d864c39","tid":1163594,"uid":87394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T14:12:08.000Z","msg":"Post下班女先"},{"pid":"a594ab967f528c7484812ec1027469b1ad34fb7e","tid":1163594,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T14:15:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://iill.li/iiḷiịiiịḷ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fiill.li%2Fii%E1%B8%B7i%E1%BB%8Bii%E1%BB%8B%E1%B8%B7&h=6f99e780&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《防彈新人王》bts 7人坐嘅位置"},{"pid":"c5127d3a4e9224bece5ea6092ccf9db077434a01","tid":1163594,"uid":76632,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"2af014d2a4b1b2715c65bebf0e3e848f9d864c39","tid":1163594,"uid":87394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T14:12:08.000Z","msg":"Post下班女先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T14:21:14.000Z","msg":"部分娛樂台成員非常變態，我驚佢地會出言不遜及對女army意淫（例如想炒飯炒麵炒粉）。<br />\n<br />\n為保障男女army以及驚自爆，所以唔會貼食客個樣。"},{"pid":"791bc2908e9fe7a53d6f7127f5898eea53a852cd","tid":1163594,"uid":221236,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T14:38:40.000Z","msg":"樓主係army<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9261ae61bf8f32cfa9554538e8086afe1c949ec8","tid":1163594,"uid":43061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T14:40:27.000Z","msg":"直接去野食圖啦"},{"pid":"17c53067dbeb34986fabbf22132499b5d3e17ab9","tid":1163594,"uid":76632,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T14:53:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://iill.li/iiḷiịiili\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fiill.li%2Fii%E1%B8%B7i%E1%BB%8Biili&h=e8c6aa47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n防彈套餐（Bangtan Set），黑豬肉泡菜撈飯+大醬湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\nBTS成員曾表示食堂是媽媽做飯的味道。<br />\n<br />\n我就覺得個大醬湯偏鹹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n而個豬肉飯睇落去平平無奇，但其實味道豐富極具內涵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，正如我老友RM一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"837b2aaf4db64b3297fba5e946bfec141acfbc0e","tid":1163594,"uid":221236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17c53067dbeb34986fabbf22132499b5d3e17ab9","tid":1163594,"uid":76632,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T14:53:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://iill.li/iiḷiịiili\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fiill.li%2Fii%E1%B8%B7i%E1%BB%8Biili&h=e8c6aa47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n防彈套餐（Bangtan Set），黑豬肉泡菜撈飯+大醬湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\nBTS成員曾表示食堂是媽媽做飯的味道。<br />\n<br />\n我就覺得個大醬湯偏鹹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n而個豬肉飯睇落去平平無奇，但其實味道豐富極具內涵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，正如我老友RM一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T14:55:42.000Z","msg":"樓主仲有冇食其他野"},{"pid":"ec2c83bc7621ba7e9b79100d3d790ac723ff72c7","tid":1163594,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T15:09:58.000Z","msg":"似乎冇人關心店長訪問及女army感受，咁我聽朝訓醒先打文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n埋完單臨走前，店長話同我傾得好投契，送咗d咖啡杯holder俾我同埋班army食客。<br />\n<br />\n我想要RM個嘜頭，但無奈太搶手缺貨剩底一個，而個鬼妹army都鍾意RM，我只好忍痛割愛讓RM俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n所以最後我拎咗阿V。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://iill.li/iiḷiịiilị\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fiill.li%2Fii%E1%B8%B7i%E1%BB%8Biil%E1%BB%8B&h=3c8542de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"187c82ab49ff2b16e8fc543f16aa65b375628a95","tid":1163594,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T15:13:37.000Z","msg":"少少毒..."},{"pid":"a8bf6e4efff31fd0a1f6b4ee9c4511756841017a","tid":1163594,"uid":76632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"837b2aaf4db64b3297fba5e946bfec141acfbc0e","tid":1163594,"uid":221236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17c53067dbeb34986fabbf22132499b5d3e17ab9","tid":1163594,"uid":76632,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T14:53:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://iill.li/iiḷiịiili\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fiill.li%2Fii%E1%B8%B7i%E1%BB%8Biili&h=e8c6aa47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n防彈套餐（Bangtan Set），黑豬肉泡菜撈飯+大醬湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\nBTS成員曾表示食堂是媽媽做飯的味道。<br />\n<br />\n我就覺得個大醬湯偏鹹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n而個豬肉飯睇落去平平無奇，但其實味道豐富極具內涵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，正如我老友RM一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T14:55:42.000Z","msg":"樓主仲有冇食其他野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T15:26:27.000Z","msg":"有個女army叫咗個泡菜鍋，佢話Suga鍾意食，我就食咗佢一塊泡菜。<br />\n<br />\n題外話，我之前去首爾7仔買咗支防彈咖啡，都幾苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。溝d燒酒感覺易入口d（有Irene加持，甜度大增）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://iill.li/iiḷiịiill\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fiill.li%2Fii%E1%B8%B7i%E1%BB%8Biill&h=df185a75&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ca1bdf8c2021516d97a9596aa6fd54f7b6af175","tid":1163594,"uid":221236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8bf6e4efff31fd0a1f6b4ee9c4511756841017a","tid":1163594,"uid":76632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"837b2aaf4db64b3297fba5e946bfec141acfbc0e","tid":1163594,"uid":221236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17c53067dbeb34986fabbf22132499b5d3e17ab9","tid":1163594,"uid":76632,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T14:53:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://iill.li/iiḷiịiili\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fiill.li%2Fii%E1%B8%B7i%E1%BB%8Biili&h=e8c6aa47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n防彈套餐（Bangtan Set），黑豬肉泡菜撈飯+大醬湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\nBTS成員曾表示食堂是媽媽做飯的味道。<br />\n<br />\n我就覺得個大醬湯偏鹹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n而個豬肉飯睇落去平平無奇，但其實味道豐富極具內涵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，正如我老友RM一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T14:55:42.000Z","msg":"樓主仲有冇食其他野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T15:26:27.000Z","msg":"有個女army叫咗個泡菜鍋，佢話Suga鍾意食，我就食咗佢一塊泡菜。<br />\n<br />\n題外話，我之前去首爾7仔買咗支防彈咖啡，都幾苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。溝d燒酒感覺易入口d（有Irene加持，甜度大增）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://iill.li/iiḷiịiill\" data-thum